{
  "texts": [
    "The p-value of the t-test (PVT) is calculated to check the performance of SPGGAN-TTUR for generating synthetic train and test sets images.",
    "The PVT of 68.1 ± 0.8% for the training set while 60.8 ± 1.5 for test sets are achieved which outper- formed the SPGGAN.",
    "However, SPGGAN-TTUR (Abdelhalim et al. 2021) suffers from artifacts in the generated image that need to be researched.",
    "In GANs, the choice of appropriate hyperparameters to control the discriminator and the generator is a challenging task.",
    "To address this problem, optimization techniques can be used to obtain adaptive losses for updating the weights of the generator."
  ]
}